org.jasig.cas.validation
接口 Assertion

所有已知实现类：
ImmutableAssertion
public interface Assertion

Represents a security assertion obtained from a successfully validated ticket.

从以下版本开始：
3.0
作者：
Scott Battaglia, Marvin S. Addison
另请参见：
CentralAuthenticationService.validateServiceTicket(String, org.jasig.cas.authentication.principal.Service)

方法摘要
 List<Authentication> getChainedAuthentications()
          Gets a list of all authentications that have occurred during a CAS SSO session.
 Authentication getPrimaryAuthentication()
          Gets the authentication event that is basis of this assertion.
 Service getService()
          Method to obtain the service for which we are asserting this ticket is valid for.

方法详细信息

getPrimaryAuthentication

Authentication getPrimaryAuthentication()
Gets the authentication event that is basis of this assertion.

返回：
Non-null primary authentication event.

getChainedAuthentications

List<Authentication> getChainedAuthentications()
Gets a list of all authentications that have occurred during a CAS SSO session.

返回：
Non-null, non-empty list of authentications in leaf-first order (i.e. authentications on the root ticket occur at the end).

isFromNewLogin

boolean isFromNewLogin()
True if the validated ticket was granted in the same transaction as that in which its grantor GrantingTicket was originally issued.

返回：
true if validated ticket was granted simultaneous with its grantor's issuance

getService

Service getService()
Method to obtain the service for which we are asserting this ticket is valid for.

返回：
the service for which we are asserting this ticket is valid for.
